#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:0
msgid "Selecting the domain host on Google Workspace"
msgstr "Selecteren van de domeinhost op Google Workspace"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:162
msgid ""
"Copy the content of the :guilabel:`Value` field under :guilabel:`TXT "
"record`. Leave the window open."
msgstr ""
"Kopieer de inhoud van het veld :guilabel:`Waarde` onder :guilabel:`TXT-"
"record`. Laat het venster open."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:0
msgid "Copying the TXT value on Google Workspace"
msgstr "Kopiëren van de TXT-waarde op Google Workspace"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:168
msgid ""
"Open the `database manager <https://www.odoo.com/my/databases>`_, click "
"the :icon:`fa-gear` (:guilabel:`gear`) button next to the database name and "
"select :icon:`fa-globe` :guilabel:`Domain Names`. Click :guilabel:`DNS`, "
"then :guilabel:`Add DNS record` and select :guilabel:`TXT`."
msgstr ""
"Open de `databasebeheerder <https://www.odoo.com/my/databases>`_, klik op de "
":icon:`fa-gear` (:guilabel:`tandwiel`) knop naast de databasenaam en "
"selecteer :icon:`fa-globe` :guilabel:`Domeinnamen`. Klik op :guilabel:`DNS`, "
"vervolgens op :guilabel:`DNS-record toevoegen` en selecteer :guilabel:`TXT`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:172
msgid ""
"Enter `@` in the :guilabel:`Name` field, paste the :guilabel:`Value` "
"provided by Google in the :guilabel:`Content` field, and "
"click :guilabel:`Add record`."
msgstr ""
"Voer `@` in het veld :guilabel:`Naam` in, plak de :guilabel:`Waarde` die "
"door Google is verstrekt in het veld :guilabel:`Inhoud`, en klik op "
":guilabel:`Record toevoegen`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:0
msgid "Creating a TXT record to verify domain name ownership"
msgstr "Aanmaken van een TXT-record om domeinnaam-eigendom te verifiëren"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:178
msgid ""
"Go back to Google Workspace, tick the box at the bottom, and "
"click :guilabel:`Confirm`."
msgstr ""
"Ga terug naar Google Workspace, vink het vakje onderaan aan en klik op "
":guilabel:`Bevestigen`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:181
msgid ""
"`Google Workspace Admin Help: Verify your domain with a TXT record <https://"
"support.google.com/a/answer/16018515>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Google Workspace Admin Help: Verifieer je domein met een TXT-record "
"<https://support.google.com/a/answer/16018515>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:185
msgid "Redirect emails to Gmail"
msgstr "E-mails doorsturen naar Gmail"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:187
