#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:376
msgid "SSL encryption (HTTPS protocol)"
msgstr "SSL-versleuteling (HTTPS-protocol)"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:378
msgid ""
"**SSL encryption** allows visitors to navigate a website through a secure "
"connection, which appears as the *https://* protocol at the beginning of a "
"web address rather than the non-secure *http://* protocol."
msgstr ""
"**SSL-versleuteling** stelt bezoekers in staat om veilig door een website te "
"navigeren, wat verschijnt als het *https://* protocol aan het begin van een "
"webadres in plaats van het onveilige *http://* protocol."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:382
msgid ""
"Odoo generates a separate SSL certificate for each domain :ref:`mapped to a "
"database <domain-name/db-map>` using `Let's Encrypt's certificate authority "
"and ACME protocol <https://letsencrypt.org/how-it-works/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Odoo genereert een apart SSL-certificaat voor elk domein :ref:`dat aan een "
"database is gekoppeld <domain-name/db-map>` met behulp van `Let's Encrypt's "
"certificaatautoriteit en ACME-protocol <https://letsencrypt.org/how-it-"
"works/>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:387
msgid "Certificate generation may take up to 24 hours."
msgstr "Het genereren van certificaten kan tot 24 uur duren."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:388
msgid ""
"Several attempts to validate your certificate are made for five days after "
"you map your domain name to your database."
msgstr ""
"Gedurende vijf dagen nadat je je domeinnaam aan je database hebt gekoppeld, "
"worden er meerdere pogingen gedaan om je certificaat te valideren."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:390
msgid "If you use another service, you can keep using it or change to Odoo's."
msgstr ""
"Als je een andere service gebruikt, kun je deze blijven gebruiken of "
"overschakelen naar die van Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:393
msgid ""
"No SSL certificate is generated for naked domains :dfn:`(domain names "
"without any subdomains or prefixes)`."
msgstr ""
"Voor naakte domeinen :dfn:`(domeinnamen zonder subdomeinen of voorvoegsels)` "
"wordt geen SSL-certificaat gegenereerd."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:399
msgid "Web base URL of a database"
msgstr "Web-basis-URL van een database"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:402
msgid ""
"If the Website app is installed on your database, skip this section and "
"continue from the :ref:`Map a domain name to a website <domain-name/website-"
"map>` section."
msgstr ""
"Als de Website-app is geïnstalleerd op je database, sla deze sectie dan over "
"en ga verder vanaf de sectie :ref:`Koppel een domeinnaam aan een website "
"<domain-name/website-map>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:405
msgid ""
"The *web base URL* or root URL of a database affects your main website "
"address and all the links sent to your customers (e.g., quotations, portal "
"links, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"De *web-basis-URL* of root-URL van een database bepaalt je hoofdwebsiteadres "
"en alle links die naar je klanten worden verstuurd (bv. offertes, "
"portaallinks, enz.)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:408
msgid ""
"To make your custom domain name the *web base URL* of your database, access "
"your database using your custom domain name and log in as an "
"administrator :dfn:`(a user part of the Settings access right group under "
"Administration)`."
msgstr ""
"Om je aangepaste domeinnaam de *web-basis-URL* van je database te maken, "
"open je de database met je aangepaste domeinnaam en log je in als beheerder "
":dfn:`(een gebruiker die deel uitmaakt van de toegangsrechtengroep "
"Instellingen onder Beheer)`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:413
msgid ""
"If you access your database with the original Odoo address (e.g., "
"`mycompany.odoo.com`), the *web base URL* of your database will be updated "
"accordingly. To prevent the automatic update of the *web base URL* when an "
"administrator logs in to the database, activate the :ref:`developer mode "
"<developer-mode>`, go to :menuselection:`Settings --> Technical --> System "
"Parameters --> New`, and enter `web.base.url.freeze` as the :guilabel:`Key` "
"and `True` as the :guilabel:`Value`."
msgstr ""
"Als je je database opent met het oorspronkelijke Odoo-adres (bv. "
"`mijnbedrijf.odoo.com`), wordt de *web basis-URL* van je database "
"dienovereenkomstig bijgewerkt. Om de automatische update van de *web basis-"
"URL* te voorkomen wanneer een beheerder inlogt op de database, activeer je "
"de :ref:`ontwikkelaarsmodus <developer-mode>`, ga je naar "
":menuselection:`Instellingen --> Technisch --> Systeemparameters --> Nieuw` "
"en voer je `web.base.url.freeze` in als de :guilabel:`Sleutel` en `True` als "
"de :guilabel:`Waarde`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:420
msgid ""
"You can also set the web base URL manually. To do so, activate "
"the :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>`, go to :menuselection:`Settings --"
"> Technical --> System Parameters`, and search for the `web.base.url` key "
"(create it if necessary) and enter the full address of your website as the "
"value (e.g., `https://www.yourdomain.com`). The URL must include the "
"protocol `https://` (or `http://`) and *not* end with a slash (`/`)."
msgstr ""
"Je kunt de web basis-URL ook handmatig instellen. Activeer hiervoor de "
":ref:`ontwikkelaarsmodus <developer-mode>`, ga naar "
":menuselection:`Instellingen --> Technisch --> Systeemparameters`, zoek naar "
"de sleutel `web.base.url` (maak deze aan indien nodig) en voer het volledige "
"adres van je website in als de waarde (bv. `https://www.jedomein.com`). De "
"URL moet het protocol `https://` (of `http://`) bevatten en *niet* eindigen "
"met een schuine streep (`/`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:429
msgid "Map a domain name to an Odoo website"
msgstr "Een domeinnaam toewijzen aan een Odoo-website"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:431
msgid ""
"Mapping your domain name to your website is different than mapping it to "
"your database:"
msgstr ""
"Een domeinnaam toewijzen aan je website is iets anders dan deze toewijzen "
"aan je database:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:433
msgid ""
"It defines your domain name as the main one for your website, helping search "
"engines to index your website correctly."
msgstr ""
"Het definieert je domeinnaam als de belangrijkste voor je website en helpt "
"zoekmachines om je website correct te indexeren."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:435
msgid ""
"It defines your domain name as the base URL for your database, including "
"portal links sent by email to your customers."
msgstr ""
"Het definieert je domeinnaam als de basis-URL voor je database, inclusief "
"portaallinks die per e-mail naar je klanten worden verzonden."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:437
msgid ""
"If you have multiple websites, it maps your domain name to the appropriate "
"website."
msgstr ""
"Bij meerdere websites wijst het je domeinnaam toe aan de juiste website."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:439
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`. If you have "
"multiple websites, select the one you want to configure. In "
"the :guilabel:`Domain` field, enter the address of your website (e.g., "
"`https://www.yourdomain.com`) and :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Ga naar :menuselection:`Website --> Configuratie --> Instellingen`. Als je "
"meerdere websites hebt, selecteer dan degene die je wilt configureren. Voer "
"in het veld :guilabel:`Domein` het adres van je website in (bv. `https://"
"www.jouwdomein.com`) en klik op :guilabel:`Opslaan`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:444
msgid ""
"Mapping your domain name to your Odoo website prevents Google Search from "
"indexing your original database address (e.g., `mycompany.odoo.com`)."
msgstr ""
"Een domeinnaam toewijzen aan je Odoo-website voorkomt dat Google Search je "
"oorspronkelijke databaseadres indexeert (bv. `mijnbedrijf.odoo.com`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:447
msgid ""
"If both addresses are already indexed, it may take some time before the "
"indexation of the second address is removed from Google Search. You can use "
"the `Google Search Console <https://search.google.com/search-console/"
"welcome>`_ to fix the issue."
msgstr ""
"Als beide adressen al geïndexeerd zijn, kan het enige tijd duren voordat de "
"indexering van het tweede adres uit Google Zoeken wordt verwijderd. Je kunt "
"de `Google Search Console <https://search.google.com/search-console/welcome>"
"`_ gebruiken om het probleem op te lossen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:452
msgid ""
"If you have multiple websites and companies on your database, make sure to "
"select the right :guilabel:`Company` under :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`. Doing so indicates Odoo which URL to use as "
"the :ref:`base URL <domain-name/web-base-url>` according to the company in "
"use."
msgstr ""
"Als je meerdere websites en bedrijven in je database hebt, zorg er dan voor "
"dat je het juiste :guilabel:`Bedrijf` selecteert onder "
":menuselection:`Website --> Configuratie --> Instellingen`. Hiermee geef je "
"aan Odoo aan welke URL moet worden gebruikt als de :ref:`basis-URL <domain-"
"name/web-base-url>` volgens het bedrijf dat in gebruik is."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:3
msgid "Google Search Console"
msgstr "Google Search console"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:5
msgid ""
"Google Search Console is a free web service provided by Google that allows "
"website owners to monitor, maintain, and troubleshoot their site's presence "
"in Google Search results. It offers valuable insights into how Google views "
"and interacts with your site, helping you optimize its performance."
msgstr ""
"Google Search Console is een gratis webservice van Google waarmee website-"
"eigenaren de aanwezigheid van hun site in Google-zoekresultaten kunnen "
"monitoren, onderhouden en troubleshooten. Het biedt waardevolle inzichten in "
"hoe Google je site bekijkt en ermee omgaat, waardoor je de prestaties kunt "
"optimaliseren."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:10
msgid ""
"To enable Google Search Console for your website, go to `Google Search "
"Console <https://search.google.com/search-console/welcome>`_. Then, select "
"the property type :ref:`GSC-Domain` or :ref:`GSC-URL prefix`."
msgstr ""
"Om Google Search Console voor je website in te schakelen, ga je naar `Google "
"Search Console <https://search.google.com/search-console/welcome>`_. "
"Selecteer vervolgens het type eigenschap :ref:`GSC-Domain` of :ref:`GSC-URL "
"prefix`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:None
msgid "Google Search Console domain or URL prefix"
msgstr "Google Search Console domein of URL-voorvoegsel"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:20
msgid "Domain property"
msgstr "Domeineigenschap"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:22
msgid ""
"A domain property in Search Console tracks all versions of your website, "
"including subdomains and protocols (http/https). This comprehensive view "
"allows you to analyze your overall website's search performance and make "
"informed decisions to optimize its visibility. Enter the domain, e.g., "
"`example.com` and click :guilabel:`Continue`."
msgstr ""
"Een domeineigenschap in Search Console volgt alle versies van je website, "
"inclusief subdomeinen en protocollen (http/https). Deze uitgebreide weergave "
"stelt je in staat de zoekprestaties van je gehele website te analyseren en "
"weloverwogen beslissingen te nemen om de zichtbaarheid te optimaliseren. "
"Voer het domein in, bv. `voorbeeld.com` en klik op :guilabel:`Doorgaan`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:28
msgid ""
"The domain property type can only be verified via `DNS record <https://"
"support.google.com/webmasters/answer/9008080?"
"hl=en#domain_name_verification&zippy=%2Chtml-tag>`_."
msgstr ""
"Het type domeineigenschap kan alleen worden geverifieerd via `DNS-record "
"<https://support.google.com/webmasters/answer/"
"9008080?hl=en#domain_name_verification&zippy=%2Chtml-tag>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:30
msgid ""
"Google suggests creating at least one domain property to represent your "
"site, as it is the most complete view of your website information."
msgstr ""
"Google raadt aan om minimaal één domeineigenschap te maken om je site te "
"vertegenwoordigen, omdat dit de meest complete weergave van je website-"
"informatie is."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:36
msgid "URL prefix property"
msgstr "URL-voorvoegsel eigenschap"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:38
msgid ""
"This type of verification is usually simpler as you have multiple "
"verification methods, such as using your existing Google Analytics or Tag "
"Manager account. It also makes sense to view a section of your website "
"separately. For example, if you work with a consultant on a specific part of "
"your website, you might want to verify this part separately to limit access "
"to your data. Enter the URL, e.g., `https://example.odoo.com/` and "
"click :guilabel:`Continue`."
msgstr ""
"Dit type verificatie is meestal eenvoudiger omdat je meerdere "
"verificatiemethoden hebt, zoals het gebruik van je bestaande Google "
"Analytics- of Tag Manager-account. Het is ook zinvol om een deel van je "
"website afzonderlijk te bekijken. Als je bijvoorbeeld met een consultant aan "
"een specifiek deel van je website werkt, wil je dit deel misschien apart "
"verifiëren om de toegang tot je gegevens te beperken. Voer de URL in, bv. "
"`https://voorbeeld.odoo.com/` en klik op :guilabel:`Doorgaan`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:46
msgid "Site ownership verification"
msgstr "Websiteeigendomsverificatie"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:48
msgid ""
"Before using Google Search Console for your website, you must verify your "
"site ownership. This verification process is a security measure that "
"protects both you and Google. It ensures that only authorized users have "
"access to sensitive data and that you have control over how your website is "
"treated in Google Search."
msgstr ""
"Voordat je Google Search Console voor je website kunt gebruiken, moet je je "
"website-eigendom verifiëren. Dit verificatieproces is een "
"veiligheidsmaatregel die zowel jou als Google beschermt. Het zorgt ervoor "
"dat alleen geautoriseerde gebruikers toegang hebben tot gevoelige gegevens "
"en dat je controle hebt over hoe je website wordt behandeld in Google Search."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:53
msgid "Five methods are available to do this:"
msgstr "Er zijn vijf methoden beschikbaar om dit te doen:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:57
msgid ":ref:`GSC-HTML-file-upload`"
msgstr ":ref:`GSC-HTML-file-upload`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:58
msgid ""
"`DNS record <https://support.google.com/webmasters/answer/9008080?"
"hl=en#domain_name_verification&zippy=%2Chtml-tag>`_"
msgstr ""
"`DNS-record <https://support.google.com/webmasters/answer/"
"9008080?hl=en#domain_name_verification&zippy=%2Chtml-tag>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:59
msgid ""
"`HTML tag <https://support.google.com/webmasters/answer/9008080?"
"hl=en#meta_tag_verification&zippy=%2Chtml-tag>`_"
msgstr ""
"`HTML-label <https://support.google.com/webmasters/answer/"
"9008080?hl=en#meta_tag_verification&zippy=%2Chtml-tag>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:60
msgid ""
"`Google Analytics tracking code <https://support.google.com/webmasters/"
"answer/9008080?hl=en#google_analytics_verification>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Google Analytics-trackingcode <https://support.google.com/webmasters/answer/"
"9008080?hl=en#google_analytics_verification>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:61
msgid ""
"`Google Tag Manager container snippet <https://support.google.com/webmasters/"
"answer/9008080?hl=en#google_tag_manager_verification>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Google Tag Manager-containersnippet <https://support.google.com/webmasters/"
"answer/9008080?hl=en#google_tag_manager_verification>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:64
msgid ""
"The best method for you depends on your comfort level and technical "
"expertise. For beginners, using a file upload or HTML tag might be easiest. "
"Those options are convenient if you already use :ref:`Google Analytics "
"<analytics/google-analytics>` or :ref:`Google Tag Manager <analytics/google-"
"tag-manager>`. You need to access your domain registrar's settings for "
"domain verification."
msgstr ""
"De beste methode voor jou hangt af van je comfortniveau en technische "
"expertise. Voor beginners is het gebruik van een bestandsupload of HTML-"
"label wellicht het makkelijkst. Die opties zijn handig als je al "
":ref:`Google Analytics <analytics/google-analytics>` of :ref:`Google Tag "
"Manager <analytics/google-tag-manager>` gebruikt. Voor domeinverificatie "
"moet je toegang hebben tot de instellingen van je domeinregistrar."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:73
msgid "HTML file upload"
msgstr "HTML-bestandsupload"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:75
msgid ""
"This method involves uploading an HTML file provided by Google containing "
"the verification code you have to put in your Odoo's Website Settings. "
"Google verifies ownership by checking for this code."
msgstr ""
"Deze methode houdt in dat je een HTML-bestand uploadt dat Google levert en "
"dat de verificatiecode bevat die je in de website-instellingen van Odoo moet "
"plaatsen. Google verifieert het eigendom door te controleren op deze code."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:78
msgid ""
"Once you added your website URL under the URL prefix option and "
"clicked :guilabel:`continue`, expand the HTML file section where you find a "
"download :icon:`fa-download` button."
msgstr ""
"Nadat je je website-URL hebt toegevoegd onder de URL-prefixoptie en op "
":guilabel:`doorgaan` hebt geklikt, vouw je de HTML-bestandssectie uit waar "
"je een downloadknop :icon:`fa-download` vindt."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:0
msgid "HTML file download"
msgstr "HTML-bestandsdownload"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:84
msgid ""
"Download your HTML verification file and copy the verification code (e.g., "
"`google123abc.html`)."
msgstr ""
"Download je HTML-verificatiebestand en kopieer de verificatiecode (bv. "
"`google123abc.html`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:0
msgid "Open and copy html file"
msgstr "HTML-bestand openen en kopiëren"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:89
msgid ""
"In your Odoo database, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`, and enable :guilabel:`Google Search Console` in "
"the :guilabel:`SEO` section. Paste the verification code (e.g., "
"`google123abc.html`) in the dedicated field."
msgstr ""
"Ga in je Odoo-database naar :menuselection:`Website --> Configuratie --> "
"Instellingen` en schakel :guilabel:`Google Search Console` in bij het "
"gedeelte :guilabel:`SEO`. Plak de verificatiecode (bv. `google123abc.html`) "
"in het daarvoor bestemde veld."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:0
msgid "Paste html code in Odoo"
msgstr "HTML-code in Odoo plakken"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:96
msgid ""
"In Google Search Console, click :guilabel:`Verify`. If you perform the steps "
"above correctly, verification should be done immediately."
msgstr ""
"Klik in Google Search Console op :guilabel:`Verifiëren`. Als je de "
"bovenstaande stappen correct uitvoert, zou de verificatie onmiddellijk "
"moeten gebeuren."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:102
msgid "HTML tag"
msgstr "HTML-label"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:104
msgid ""
"This method involves copying a meta tag provided by Google and pasting it "
"into your Odoo website. To verify your site ownership using an HTML tag, "
"follow these instructions:"
msgstr ""
"Deze methode houdt in dat je een metatag kopieert die Google levert en deze "
"in je Odoo-website plakt. Volg deze instructies om je website-eigendom te "
"verifiëren met behulp van een HTML-label:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:107
msgid "Expand the HTML tag section."
msgstr "Vouw de HTML-labelsectie uit."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:0
msgid "Open HTML tag section."
msgstr "Open de HTML-labelsectie."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:112
msgid ":guilabel:`Copy` the HTML tag to clipboard."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Kopieer` het HTML-label naar het klembord."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:113
msgid ""
"On your Odoo website, click :guilabel:`Edit` in the upper-right corner, go "
"to the :guilabel:`Theme` tab, scroll down to the :guilabel:`Advanced` "
"section, then click :guilabel:`<head> and </body>` next to :guilabel:`Code "
"Injection`. Paste the copied tag into the first field (:guilabel:`<head>`), "
"and click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Klik op je Odoo-website op :guilabel:`Bewerken` in de rechterbovenhoek, ga "
"naar het tabblad :guilabel:`Thema`, scroll naar beneden naar de sectie "
":guilabel:`Geavanceerd` en klik vervolgens op :guilabel:`<head> en </body>` "
"naast :guilabel:`Code-injectie`. Plak het gekopieerde label in het eerste "
"veld (:guilabel:`<head>`) en klik op :guilabel:`Opslaan`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:0
msgid "Paste tag in head field."
msgstr "Plak het label in het head-veld."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:121
msgid ""
"Return to :abbr:`GSC (Google Search Console)` and click :guilabel:`Verify`."
msgstr ""
"Ga terug naar :abbr:`GSC (Google Search Console)` en klik op "
":guilabel:`Verifiëren`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:124
msgid ":doc:`domain_names`"
msgstr ":doc:`domain_names`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo allows you to create multiple websites from the same database. This can "
"be useful, for example, if you have multiple brands operating under your "
"organization, or to create separate websites for different products/"
"services, or different audiences. In these cases, having different websites "
"can help avoid confusion and make it easier to tailor your digital outreach "
"strategies and reach your target audience."
msgstr ""
"Met Odoo kun je meerdere websites maken vanuit dezelfde database. Dit kan "
"bijvoorbeeld handig zijn als je meerdere merken hebt die onder je "
"organisatie vallen, of om aparte websites te maken voor verschillende "
"producten/diensten of verschillende doelgroepen. In deze gevallen kan het "
"hebben van verschillende websites helpen verwarring te voorkomen en het "
"gemakkelijker maken om je digitale publieksbereikstrategieën aan te passen "
"en je doelgroep te bereiken."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:11
msgid ""
"Each website can be designed and configured independently with its "
"own :doc:`domain name <domain_names>`, :doc:`theme <../web_design/"
"themes>`, :doc:`pages <../structure/pages>`, :doc:`menus <../structure/"
"header_footer>`, :doc:`languages <translate>`, :doc:`products <../../"
"ecommerce/products>`, assigned sales team, etc. They can also :ref:`share "
"content and pages <multi-website/website_content>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:18
msgid ""
"Duplicate content (i.e., pages and content shared between multiple websites) "
"can have a negative impact on :doc:`../structure/seo`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:22
msgid "Website creation"
msgstr "Website maken"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:24
msgid "To create a new website, proceed as follows:"
msgstr "Ga als volgt te werk om een nieuwe website te maken:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:27
msgid "Click :guilabel:`+ New Website`."
msgstr "Klik op :guilabel:`+ Nieuwe website`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:0
msgid "New website button"
msgstr "Knop Nieuwe website"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:32
msgid ""
"Specify the :guilabel:`Website Name` and :guilabel:`Website domain`. Each "
"website must be published under its own :doc:`domain <domain_names>`."
msgstr ""
"Geef de :guilabel:`Websitenaam` en het :guilabel:`Websitedomein` op. Elke "
"website moet onder zijn eigen :doc:`domein <domain_names>` worden "
"gepubliceerd."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:34
msgid ""
"Adapt the :guilabel:`Company name`, :guilabel:`Languages` "
"and :guilabel:`Default language` if needed."
msgstr ""
"Pas de :guilabel:`Bedrijfsnaam`, :guilabel:`Talen` en "
":guilabel:`Standaardtaal` aan indien nodig."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:36
msgid "Click the :guilabel:`Create` button."
msgstr "Klik op de knop :guilabel:`Aanmaken`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:38
msgid "You can then start building your new website."
msgstr "Je kunt dan beginnen met het bouwen van je nieuwe website."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:41
msgid ""
"By default, all website-related apps that you have installed (e.g. "
"**eCommerce**, **Forum**, **Blog**, etc.) and their related website pages "
"are also available on the new website. You can remove them by amending the "
"website's menu."
msgstr ""
"Standaard zijn alle website-gerelateerde apps die je hebt geïnstalleerd (bv. "
"**E-commerce**, **Forum**, **Blog**, enz.) en hun bijbehorende "
"websitepagina's ook beschikbaar op de nieuwe website. Je kunt ze verwijderen "
"door het menu van de website aan te passen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:46
msgid "Switching websites"
msgstr "Tussen websites wisselen"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:48
msgid ""
"To switch from one website to another, click the menu next to "
"the :guilabel:`+New` button in the top right corner and select the website "
"you want to switch to."
msgstr ""
"Om van de ene website naar de andere te wisselen, klik je op het menu naast "
"de knop :guilabel:`+Nieuw` in de rechterbovenhoek en selecteer je de website "
"waarnaar je wilt wisselen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:None
msgid "Website selector"
msgstr "Websitekiezer"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:55
msgid ""
"When you switch websites, you are redirected to the homepage of the other "
"website."
msgstr ""
"Wanneer je van website wisselt, word je doorgestuurd naar de startpagina van "
"de andere website."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:58
msgid "Website-specific configuration"
msgstr "Websitespecifieke configuratie"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:60
msgid ""
"Most website settings are website-specific, which means they can be enabled/"
"disabled per website. To adapt the settings for a website, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`. Select the "
"desired website in the field :guilabel:`Settings of Website` at the top of "
"the :guilabel:`Settings` page, in the **yellow** banner. Then, adapt the "
"options for that specific website."
msgstr ""
"De meeste website-instellingen zijn websitespecifiek, wat betekent dat ze "
"per website kunnen worden in-/uitgeschakeld. Om de instellingen voor een "
"website aan te passen, ga je naar :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Configuratie --> Instellingen`. Selecteer de gewenste website in het veld "
":guilabel:`Instellingen van website` bovenaan de pagina "
":guilabel:`Instellingen`, in de **gele** banner. Pas vervolgens de opties "
"voor die specifieke website aan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:67
msgid ""
"Websites are created with the default settings; the settings are not copied "
"from one website to the other."
msgstr ""
"Websites worden gemaakt met de standaardinstellingen; de instellingen worden "
"niet van de ene website naar de andere gekopieerd."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:69
msgid ""
"In a :doc:`multi-company environment </applications/general/companies>`, "
"each website can be linked to a specific company in your database so that "
"only company-related data (e.g., products, jobs, events, etc.) is displayed "
"on the website. To display company-specific data, set the desired company in "
"the :guilabel:`Company` field."
msgstr ""
"In een :doc:`omgeving met meerdere bedrijven </applications/general/"
"companies>` kan elke website worden gekoppeld aan een specifiek bedrijf in "
"je database, zodat alleen bedrijfsgerelateerde gegevens (bv. producten, "
"vacatures, evenementen, enz.) op de website worden weergegeven. Om "
"bedrijfsspecifieke gegevens weer te geven, stel je het gewenste bedrijf in "
"het veld :guilabel:`Bedrijf` in."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:77
msgid "Content availability"
msgstr "Beschikbaarheid van inhoud"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:79
msgid ""
"By default, pages, products, events, etc. created from the frontend (using "
"the :guilabel:`+New` button) are only available on the website from which it "
"was created. Records created from the backend, however, are made available "
"on all websites by default. The content's availability can be changed in the "
"backend, in the :guilabel:`Website` field. For example, for products, go "
"to :menuselection:`eCommerce --> Products`, then select the product and go "
"to the :guilabel:`Sales` tab. For forums, go "
"to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Forums`, then select the forum."
msgstr ""
"Standaard zijn pagina's, producten, evenementen, enz. die vanaf de frontend "
"zijn aangemaakt (met de :guilabel:`+Nieuw`-knop) alleen beschikbaar op de "
"website waarop ze zijn aangemaakt. Records die vanuit de backend zijn "
"aangemaakt, zijn echter standaard op alle websites beschikbaar. De "
"beschikbaarheid van de inhoud kun je wijzigen in de backend, in het "
":guilabel:`Website`-veld. Voor producten ga je bijvoorbeeld naar "
":menuselection:`E-commerce --> Producten`, selecteer je het product en ga je "
"naar het tabblad :guilabel:`Verkoop`. Voor forums ga je naar "
":menuselection:`Configuratie --> Forums` en selecteer je het forum."

